⚠️ Microcurrent on the go? 
Yes you can!

☆ Ziip - Nanocurrent™ and Microcurrent Spot Treatment Device.
First of all how cute is this design? Small yet effective 👌 

- Designed to treat spots in 90 seconds
- Calming and reduce irritation on the skin
- Rebalence the microbiomeon in your skin
- Great to take with you anywhere 
- Studies shows reductions of Inflammation by 87%

How it works? 
- Apply 2 to 3 pumps of the Clear Gel
- Press the on switch bottom and it's on Treat mode.
- Press the Dot on the desired area and move it clockwise & counterclockwise, you will feel needles sensation but don't be alarmed that's normal.
- The Dot will switch off automatically once the Treatment is done.
- You can choose a 90 second one area treatment or a 6 minutes Full face 

Recommend to use 2 to 3 times per week for best results 🤌

latestPosts.caption:
Hello Beautiful ✨️

Don't you just love discovering new perfumes? Even better if they are niche and unique 😉

We start strong with 3 fragrances from @michela_mezzetti_parfums

☆ Lick me 👅 this one is Sweet! Like eatable sweet 🤤 great projection and long lasting on my skin.
Top notes of Sugar and Whipped Cream. Heart notes of Ice Cream, Waffle Cone and Iris. To close the notes with Vanilla and Amber 🫶 This dna is my favourite when it comes to perfumes. 
100/10 ⭐️

☆ Breath me 💨 I do like the Boozy opening although it does settle into a beautiful feminine scent. Top notes with Marine Notes, Ozonic Notes, Aperol, Salt and Orange. The heart notes go from White Wine to Rose.
Amber, Poppy, Cypress as base notes.
It gives me a very confident business woman 😉
9/10 ⭐️

☆ Pop me 🍿 ok so this was an interesting one 🤭 just imagine Cinema date night 🎬
That smell of delicious popcorn but the one from the Movies. 
Top notes obviously 
Popcorn, Movie Theatre Accord.
The heart notes are Cotton Candy that it gives a twist to this fragrance.
Finally we have base notes with 
Pastry Shop Accord and Pink Icing. 
Over all i do like it but after 10 minutes on my skin. 
8/10 ⭐️

We finish today with @duduar_milano
with their perfume Vodkaviar.
I like the floral opening which was a surprise as I was expecting more of a Boozy fruity start. This one has a complex and very intriguing combination. 
Top notes with Lime, Strawberry, Grape, Kaipiroska, Pink Salt, Mandarin.
The heart notes of Chlorine, Vodka, Pink Pepper, Almond Blossom, Ginger, Cherry Blossom and Red Caviar. As I said a very intriguing blend that actually works amazing. 
The fragrance does settle with notes of Wood, Musk, Green Leaves, Amber, Gourmand. 
I personally find this one very sophisticated and elegant. 
10/10 ⭐️

Gifted/PR @edulge 🫶

Hello Beautiful 😍 

What better way to start the weekend? Opening this luxurious perfume 😍 

✨️ Commodity- Gold in Bold.

When I tried their discovery set, I was totally captivated by Gold, especially in Bold straight. 

Sweet, Spicy and Woody. Powerful spice coming from Nutmeg, Saffron and Patchouli. Yet it settles into this beautiful sweet Vanilla and Amber scent. Warm and cosy, this fragrance will totally inebriante you from the first sniff 😳

The projection is insanely good and it does last on my skin over 12hrs. Obviously it can vary from skin to skin tho, but generally this one last a long time 🫶

If you like warm, sweet and spicy fragrances, then absolutely check this one out. 
100/10 ⭐️
